    "description": "Kekmonomichi&quot; is a command action RPG.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Receive requests and search</h2>.The main character receives requests from the people of the city as a detective.<br>The game progresses by fulfilling the requests.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132010/extras/6567169b95edb230e57408a9c330a775.avif?t=1731067192\" width=500 height=280 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Command Action Battle</h2>.In this title, simple action commands are performed when attacking or defending.<br>If successful, you can increase the damage you inflict or avoid enemy attacks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132010/extras/e548d0673f395fd01350778ccda2ff9c.avif?t=1731067192\" width=500 height=280 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Preparation for search</h2>.Before going on a search, you can eat a dish to give you an advantage in your search.<br>Eat the food to get the best out of your search.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132010/extras/6cbf528b018008d819106770266f0d4f.avif?t=1731067192\" width=500 height=280 /></span><br><br>In this title, items can be made from materials obtained during the search.<br>You can also buy items from peddlers, but if you have the materials, you can make a variety of items.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132010/extras/ac06a35c20f0d8e49c3ec8455fd4dadd.avif?t=1731067192\" width=500 height=280 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Redecorate your room</h2>.You can redecorate the rooms that serve as your base.<br>For a change of scenery!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132010/extras/837ba091ffa9bff2086547dc3f9ab367.avif?t=1731067192\" width=500 height=280 /></span>",
